[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21520] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 9: <The docs here were copied from Google's Gemini, when I asked it how to generate a cpanfile>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21522] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 10: <**1. Manual Creation**>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21524] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 11: <* **Create a file named `cpanfile`:** This file will reside in the root directory of your project.>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21525] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 12: <* **Add dependencies:**>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21527] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 13: <* Each line in the `cpanfile` represents a dependency.>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21529] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 14: <* Use the following syntax: `require 'ModuleName';`>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21531] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 15: <* Example>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21532] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 16: <```perl>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21534] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 17: <require 'JSON';>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21535] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 18: <require 'Template';>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21537] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 19: <require 'DateTime';>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21539] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 20: <require 'DBIx::Class';>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21540] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 21: <```>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21542] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 22: <**2. Using `Mojolicious::Command::Author::generate::cpanfile`**>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21544] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 23: <* **Install the Mojolicious framework (if not already installed):**>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21546] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 24: <```bash>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21547] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 25: <cpanm Mojolicious>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21549] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 26: <```>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21550] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 27: <* **Generate the `cpanfile`:**>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21552] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 28: <```bash>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21554] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 29: <mojo generate cpanfile>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21556] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 30: <```>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21558] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 31: <This command analyzes your Perl source code files (usually located in the `lib` directory) to identify used modules and generates the `cpanfile` accordingly.>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21559] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 32: <**3. Using Carton**>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21561] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 33: <* **Install Carton:**>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21563] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 34: <```bash>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21564] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 35: <cpanm Carton>. token: 
[2026-07-23 12:33:31.21566] [2238301] [debug] Processing line 36: <```>. token: 
